---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us"
  description="Get in touch with Computer Science Guide. We'd love to hear your feedback, questions, or suggestions."
>
  <article class="article">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Contact Us</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          Have a question, suggestion, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you!
          Choose the best way to reach us below.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-grid">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="contact-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>General Inquiries</h2>
            <p>Questions about our guides, suggestions for new content, or general feedback.</p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@computerscienceguide.com" class="contact-link">
              hello@computerscienceguide.com
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="contact-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Privacy Concerns</h2>
            <p>Questions about your data, privacy policy, or requests to access or delete your information.</p>
            <a href="mailto:privacy@computerscienceguide.com" class="contact-link">
              privacy@computerscienceguide.com
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="contact-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Technical Issues</h2>
            <p>Report bugs, broken links, or technical problems with the website.</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@computerscienceguide.com" class="contact-link">
              support@computerscienceguide.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Response Time</h2>
        <p>
          We typically respond to all inquiries within <strong>1-2 business days</strong>.
          During busy periods, it may take up to 5 business days. Thank you for your patience!
        </p>

        <h2>Content Suggestions</h2>
        <p>
          We're always looking to improve and expand our guides. If you have suggestions for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>New topics you'd like us to cover</li>
          <li>Improvements to existing guides</li>
          <li>Corrections or updates to outdated information</li>
          <li>Resources you think we should include</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Please don't hesitate to reach out! Your feedback helps us create better content for everyone.
        </p>

        <h2>Connect With Us</h2>
        <p>
          Follow us for updates on new guides and computer science tips:
        </p>
        <div class="social-note">
          <p>
            <em>Social media profiles coming soon! For now, the best way to stay updated is to
            bookmark our site and check back regularly for new content.</em>
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>
          Before reaching out, you might find your answer in our guides:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/guides">Browse all guides</a></li>
          <li><a href="/roadmap">View the learning roadmap</a></li>
          <li><a href="/resources">Check our curated resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">Learn more about us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <style>
    .intro {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .contact-card {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-icon {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-link {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .social-note {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }

    .social-note p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
